      </p>
      <h2 class="text-center"><i class="fa fa-question-circle"></i></h2>
      <h2 class="text-center">More Questions?</h2>
      <p>
        Shoot us an <%= link_to "email", "mailto:info@itsridic.com" %> or check out the <%= link_to "Amazon product page", "http://www.amazon.com/Its-Ridic-touchscreen-texting-winter/dp/B015NB7USA" %> where some questions have already been answered.
